# 🌿 Marcy's Deck Grimoire

A personal tarot and oracle deck reference app — single HTML file, no server, no dependencies, works fully offline.

Built for a five-deck practice spanning tarot, oracle, and esoteric systems.

---

## Decks

| Deck | Type | Cards |
|---|---|---|
| Sailor Moon Tarot | Tarot | 78 |
| Erotic Tarot | Tarot | 78 |
| African Goddess Rising Oracle | Oracle | 44 |
| Kimbition Oracle | Oracle | 45 |
| Heaven & Hell Oracle | Oracle | 72 |

---

## Features

### Card Reference
- Full card list for all five decks
- Upright and reversed meanings for both tarot decks
- AGR organized by all 9 Temples with goddess meanings, shadow, and embodiment question
- Kimbition cards with spiritual/reflective interpretations
- Heaven & Hell Angel (upright) / Demon (reversed) pairs
- Deck-specific personal notes per card — Sailor Moon and Erotic Tarot store notes separately even for shared Major Arcana names
- Favorites system

### Spread Logger
- Log spreads with name, date, question, and overall question
- Add cards from any deck with position, card, orientation, and card-level notes
- Section headers to group cards within a spread (e.g. Personality / Timing / Appearance)
- Up/down buttons to reorder cards and sections
- Duplicate card rows for fast multi-card logging from the same deck
- Overall synthesis field for your personal reading of the full spread
- 10 built-in spread templates including FS Spread, Celtic Cross, Ancestral Council, and Soul Map

### Tagging
19 tags for pull history filtering:
💗 Love · 🌑 Shadow · ✨ Career · 🌸 Spirit · 🌿 Body · 🌊 Ancestors · ⏳ Timing · 🔮 General · 🎉 Fun · 🤝 Social · ✈ Travel · 🌙 Fantasy · 🌹 Erotic · 🤍 Grief · 💰 Money · 🌱 Health · 📋 Past · 🌠 Future · 💜 Dream

### Pull History
- Search across all spreads, positions, cards, notes, and tags
- Filter by deck and by tag
- Sort by newest, oldest, most cards, least cards
- Paginated — 8 spreads per page
- Expand/collapse individual spread entries
- Collapsible sections within sectioned spreads
- Edit and clone existing spreads

### Stats
- Total spreads and per-deck counts
- Most Pulled Cards — top 8 cards with upright/reversed orientation breakdown and visual bar
- Card History Search — find every spread a specific card appeared in, with summary counts and orientation split

### Navigation
- Sticky nav bar stays visible while scrolling
- Jump-to nav within Sailor Moon, Erotic Tarot, and AGR to skip to a suit or temple
- Back to top button appears after scrolling

### Data
- All data stored in browser localStorage
- Export to JSON backup
- Import from JSON backup
- Clear all data option

---

## Usage

1. Download `deck_grimoire.html`
2. Open it in any modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
3. No internet connection required after download

That's it. There is no build step, no install, no server.

---

## Data Persistence

All pull history, card notes, and favorites are stored in your **browser's localStorage**. This means:

- Data is tied to the specific browser you use
- Clearing browser data will erase it
- Opening the file in a different browser or device starts fresh

**Recommendation:** Use the Export Data button regularly and save backups to a cloud folder (Google Drive, iCloud, etc.) alongside the HTML file. Use Import Data to restore on a new device or browser.

