## Five-Deck System

| Deck | Role |
|---|---|
| 🌙 Sailor Moon Tarot | Main narrative of the reading |
| 💋 Erotic Tarot | Erotic archetypes and energetic dynamics |
| 🌺 African Goddess Rising | Spiritual authority — always has the final word |
| 🌶 Kimbition Oracle | Fantasy, desire, and power dynamics |
| 😇👿 Heaven & Hell | Alignment vs distortion — highest vs shadow expression |

